A summary of the club's achievements over the last week üßä :

1. [Baron's X](https://x.com/BaronHatter) account has been subscribed to by Luca Netz. This allows direct communication with Luca on Twitter, making communication easier.

2. Baron [purchased NFT](https://t.me/clubigloo/82) from the Lil Pudgys collection, which opened up new features - holder chats, subscriptions and social contacts. üèé

Dubai Token 2049 **üöÄ**:
It was important for us to follow the PP team inside this event. So with the help of many of our club residents and their friends, we were able to gather some interesting talking points from this event:

1. There will definitely be more PP sticker collections as interest in them is only increasing. Our club even did a poll on what collection we would like to see next. The interest in stickers is fuelled by PP themselves, for example, [Luca's post.](https://t.me/lucanetztg/37) 

2. PP`s stickers are very actively handled by Ton's staff and RR's Asian team. So it is a product of both teams specifically, not just "stickers inside a telegram". We have a specific list of individuals that we will not share publicly, in order to prevent spam to them. We are already using this list to invite specific guests to the AMA session where we will be revealing the actors.

3. Improving and adding rarity to PP stickers will. This information was also confirmed indirectly by [Luca with his post](https://t.me/lucanetztg/37)

4. The @penguclash game was made by the sticker team, however, there is no integration between these products beforehand. But still this game will be the first narrative between Ton and Ethereum (telegram and X), as in X it is gaining very [big support](https://x.com/PenguClash)  from PP officials (in telegram it is also promoted by Luka). So we are waiting for western guests in our spaces and chats. 
5. In addition to attributes, stickers are waiting for more interesting and complex mechanisms that will definitely please the community and increase the value of NFT. 
6. The PP team is reluctant to do in-person interviews, but we are already building social bridges through connected people to get an official AMA session. 

üöÄ New club residents: 
- Many Influencers on Tone [(Zenith,](https://x.com/ZenithTON) [Jeribond](https://x.com/0xweb3bond) , [MF.](https://x.com/mfckr_eth?s=21) [Echo.](http://t.me/echoington) Have identified points of interest with some of the guys through networking and want to do joint AMA sessions 
- Ton staff. Our club now has direct PP product developers represented by Ton staff.
- team @alphakek (Pengu AI) - mega cool connections with AI developers for leading brands in the Web3 sphere. Special thanks to Vladimir from the team for useful information. 

Also thanks for responsiveness and help in gathering information to other residents of the club: [Echo,](http://t.me/echoington) [cuteinvestments](https://t.me/cutejpegsru)
